text: Humppila is a municipality in Kanta-Häme, Finland. About 2,460 people lived there in 2013. The municipalities next to it are Forssa, Jokioinen, Ypäjä, Loimaa, Punkalaidun and Urjala. Humppila was established in 1874. ==Distances== * Helsinki 130 km * Turkuun 85 km * Poriin 105 km * Tampere 70 km ==Villages== Vitikka, Huhtaa, Humppila, Koivisto, Murto, Taipale, Venäjä and Myllynkulma. ==Other websites== * Homepage Category:Municipalities of Kanta-Häme
